column3: For the years ended June 30, 2021 (“fiscal 2021”), June 30, 2020 (“fiscal 2020”), and June 30, 2019 (“fiscal 2019”), Professional Employer Organization (“PEO”) revenues are net of direct pass-through costs, primarily consisting of payroll wages and payroll taxes, of $51,362.3 million, $45,826.1 million, and $42,688.8 million, respectively.
